data.description: Well maintained Sweetwater / Cordry home with an assumable 2.25 % mortgage! Pride of ownership is abundant from the moment upon entering this warm home. Step inside two story great room with large upper level height windows. Enjoy the natural light and the moon that is showcased within the window. A nice unexpected touch! The great room fireplace offers a brick facing complimented with a warm light and bright kitchen with light oak mantle. Adjoining eat in dining area is right off the well appointed with maple cabinets and stainless steel appliances. The primary bedroom and bath are configured in an en-suite with a roomy jetted tub.  The two story loft is tailor made for multiple uses, a home office, kids study area, you decide!. Main level bedroom with large closet is perfect for any age. Huge outdoor deck area with views of Sweetwater Lake offer awesome entertaining seasonal options. From the warm Spring season to The Brown County Fall changing colors, you will love grilling or watching the starry skies. Sellers are leaving the deck canopy and umbrella. This home has a nice sized mini barn for storage and is well positioned on 2 lots that total nearly 3/4 of an acre. All this and full lake privileges on the two clearest lakes in all of the state! Swim, boat, ski, tube and fish, an awesome opportunity! An easy and short walk to Sweetwater beach and the hiking trails are just a few minutes away. Schedule your appointment today!
